main event: A report regarding a UFO sighting involving a small white light observed by a witness in July 1964.
interesting points: The object emitted a very bright light and was observed moving from west to east at a very high speed., The sighting lasted for a period of two minutes., The report was part of the Project Blue Book investigations by the U.S. Air Force., The object was sighted from coordinates 36-59N 175-30W., No photographs or physical evidence were recorded in the reports.
witness description: an observer from the reported coordinates
